{
  "id": "69d63cee393463b5c371d53b",
  "title": "大人ぶろうとするより子供っぽいほうが却って良い説",
  "created": 1775647987,
  "updated": 1775654947,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69d63cee393463b5c371d53b",
      "text": "大人ぶろうとするより子供っぽいほうが却って良い説",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775647987,
      "updated": 1775648041
    },
    {
      "id": "69d63cf300000000006afdd9",
      "text": "from [宝くじ仮説ってなんだ]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775647987,
      "updated": 1775648023
    },
    {
      "id": "69d63cfe00000000006afdda",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775647999,
      "updated": 1775647999
    },
    {
      "id": "69d63d2a00000000006afddc",
      "text": "ちゃんと調べて嘘か真か調べるんやで[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775648043,
      "updated": 1775648047
    },
    {
      "id": "69d63d2b00000000006afddd",
      "text": " え〜[caki.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775648043,
      "updated": 1775648047
    },
    {
      "id": "69d63d2b00000000006afdde",
      "text": "  わかった！",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775648043,
      "updated": 1775648047
    },
    {
      "id": "69d63d2b00000000006afddf",
      "text": "  えらい[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775648043,
      "updated": 1775648047
    },
    {
      "id": "69d63d2b00000000006afde0",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775648043,
      "updated": 1775648043
    },
    {
      "id": "69d63d2f00000000006afde1",
      "text": "可愛い子供みたいなリアクションをすると許され度が上がる",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775648048,
      "updated": 1775648087
    },
    {
      "id": "69d63d5800000000006afde4",
      "text": "\tクソガキじゃなくて可愛い子供のマネ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775648088,
      "updated": 1775648107
    },
    {
      "id": "69d63d7100000000006afde5",
      "text": "\t理屈をこねて大人っぽくしようとする / 頑張って言いくるめようとするよりも、",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775648114,
      "updated": 1775648229
    },
    {
      "id": "69d63de800000000006afde8",
      "text": "\t\t何も意味のある言葉を言っていないにも関わらず、良い感じにやり取りが進む",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775648233,
      "updated": 1775654947
    },
    {
      "id": "69d63d770000000000f9b9e5",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1775648119,
      "updated": 1775648119
    },
    {
      "id": "69d63d770000000000f9b9e6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1775648119,
      "updated": 1775648119
    },
    {
      "id": "69d63d780000000000f9b9e7",
      "text": "[大人ぶろうとするより子供っぽいほうが却って良い説（脱線）]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1775648120,
      "updated": 1775651892
    }
  ]
